name: Cute_CN_Girl_2
description:
训练集来源于网络爬取图片，使用时请参考我的提示词。

The training set is from the network crawl picture, please refer to my prompt words when using.

底模chilloutmix_Ni

The base-model is chilloutmix_Ni.

qincai,1girl即为触发词。

qincai and 1girl were trigger words.

本lora的特点是头发好看，光影感真实，输出的时候脸部会占比较大，想出全身图可以把full body权重调高。

The features of this LoRa are beautiful hair and real sense of light and shadow. When output, the face will take up a large proportion, and the weight of the full body can be adjusted higher by coming up with the whole body picture.

提示词中的“ulzzang-6500”或者“pureerosface”为文本反转模型，请自行下载。

"ulzzang-6500" or "pureerosface" in the prompt word is a text reversal model. Please download it yourself.

全身图容易崩脸，使用SwinIR_4x高清修复即可，如果你没有这个选项，可以在WEBUI-选项-Stable Diffusion里面勾选上“Upcast cross attention layer to float32”(在页面最底端)

Full body pictures are easy to crack,Use SwinIR_4x HD to fix it. If you don't have this option, check "Upcast cross attention layer to float32" in webu-Options-stable Diffusion.

这是本人的第二个三次元真人lora，如果觉得效果可以，请给我一个关注和赞。

This is my second three-dimensional real person lora. If you think the effect is OK, please give me your subscribe and praise.

需要我帮忙练三次元lora也可以联系我。

Please contact me if you need my help to train a 3D real person LoRa
